===拍攝===
[[File:Carey_Mulligan_2009.jpg|thumb]]在劇中飾演莎莉·斯帕洛一角。這角色使她後來問鼎加拿大{{link-en|星座獎|Constellation Awards}}的最佳女主角獎。]]

《眨眼》的導演為{{link-en|希提·麥克唐納|Hettie MacDonald}}，她是繼1985年的《{{link-en|王妃的標誌|The Mark of the Rani}}》後首位替《異世奇人》執導的女性<ref>{{cite web|last=Jusino|first=Teresa|title=Moffat's Woman #3 – Sally|url=http://www.tor.com/blogs/2010/01/moffats-women-3-sally|work=Tor.com|publisher=Macmillan Publishers|accessdate=7-8-2012|date=2010-01-27|archive-date=2013-05-14|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6GbkgWiPH?url=http://www.tor.com/blogs/2010/01/moffats-women-3-sally|dead-url=no}}</ref>。監制[[拉塞爾·T·戴維斯|羅素·T·戴維斯]]指麥克唐納的到來使得劇集加入了「最美的視覺效果」，而且是「前所未有的」<ref name="commentary"/>。在選角方面，劇組起用[[嘉莉·慕萊根|嘉莉·慕萊根]]擔當女主角。在得悉獲得參演機會後，穆里根狂喜。另一方面，她最初對[[大衛·田納特|大衛·田納特]]的出鏡次數表示關注，但劇集播出後，她還是感到滿意的<ref name="commentary"/>。

本劇的取景地點眾多，在劇中出現的警局場景拍攝於2006年11月21日，地點為[[卡迪夫|卡迪夫]]的[[煤炭交易所|煤炭交易所]]和斯圖爾特山廣場<ref>{{cite web|url= http://www.bbc.co.uk/wales/arts/sites/doctor-who-wales/alllocations/cardiff-coal-exchange-mount-stuart-square|title= Walesarts, Coal Exchange and Mount Stuart Square, Cardiff Bay|work= BBC – Wales|publisher= [[BBC|BBC]]|accessdate= 2010-05-30|archive-date= 2012-05-08|archive-url= https://www.webcitation.org/67V2nGv5Q?url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/wales/arts/sites/doctor-who-wales/alllocations/cardiff-coal-exchange-mount-stuart-square|dead-url= no}}</ref>。空屋在劇中雖號稱位於[[倫敦|倫敦]]，而事實上，這是取景自[[紐波特|紐波特]]西部一間荒廢的房子<ref name="confidential"/>。儘管房子內部已日久失收，但劇組在拍攝時只對進行很少的粉飾<ref name="commentary"/>。莫法特事後也被屋子的荒涼嚇怕，更稱這是他見過以後「最令人毛骨悚然的房子」<ref name="commentary"/>。飾演拉里的芬利則把屋子比作為[[史酷比|史酷比]]的房子，蓋因這卡通片時常出現主角們入住荒廢住所的劇情<ref>Russell, p. 187</ref>。[[BBC|BBC]]其後透露，1969年即博士、鐘斯和比利被困的那一年，也正好是[[叔比狗，你在哪裡！|叔比狗，你在哪裡！]]首播的年份<ref name="factfile">{{cite web|first=Peter|last=Ware|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/doctorwho/episodes/2007/facts/fact_310.shtml|title=Doctor Who – Fact File – "Blink"|publisher=[[BBC|BBC]]|accessdate=9-6-2007|archive-date=2013-04-20|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6G17OWe4X?url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/doctorwho/episodes/2007/facts/fact_310.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

原來，劇組打算由{{link-en|米高·奧比奧拉|Michael Obiora}}分演年青和年老的比利。然而，劇組認為奧比奧拉的老妝實在太不真實，於是劇組別外選用了{{link-en|路易士·馬奧斯|Louis Mahoney}}扮演老比利一角。 另一個問題也隨之而來﹕奧比奧拉是倫敦腔的，而馬奧斯則是重口音。為解決這問題，奧比奧拉需使改變其口音朗讀對白<ref name="commentary"/>。另外，比利在劇中提到[[TARDIS|TARDIS]]的玻璃與真的警察電話亭不一。玻璃大小的問題早於2004年時已被討論過，當時，《異世奇人》的觀眾就指TARDIS的玻璃實在太大<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.gallifreyone.com/forum/showpost.php?p=4161263&postcount=177 |title=Re: Moffat hates fans? |accessdate=12-6-2007 |last=Moffat |first=Steven |authorlink=Steven Moffat |date=12-6-2007 |publisher=Shaun Lyon |quote=I put in the Windows gag SPECIFICALLY to make this forum laugh. It was for us lot here — the rest of the world didn't notice. |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070930202521/http://www.gallifreyone.com/forum/showpost.php?p=4161263&postcount=177 |archivedate=2007-09-30 |deadurl=yes }} {{subscription required}}</ref>。

===效果===
莫法特笑言﹕「當我還是兒時早已設計不少《異世奇人》的怪物。現在，我真的把牠們做了出來，這使得美術部花了不少的錢」<ref name="confidential"/>。為使哭泣天使看來像堅硬的石像，化妝師把布料浸在玻璃纖維樹脂裹，然後塗上顏料<ref name="confidential"/>。另一方面，雖然哭泣天使在劇中很少活動，但這些外星怪物都是由化了妝的真人飾演<ref name=russell>Russell, p. 186</ref><ref name="confidential">{{cite episode |title=Do You Remember the First Time? |series=[[Doctor_Who_Confidential|Doctor Who Confidential]] |network=[[BBC|BBC]] |station=[[BBC_Three|BBC Three]] |city=Cardiff |airdate=9-6-2007|seriesno=3|number=10}}</ref>。兩名演員阿迦·布朗斯卡（Aga Blonska）和艾倫·湯馬士分別戴上不同的面具，前者看來較為馴和，後者面目猙獰<ref name="confidential"/>。布朗斯卡稱雖然他化了妝，又被塗上油漆，但他還是演出很舒服<ref name=radiotimesangels>{{cite web|title=Creating the Weeping Angel|url=http://old.radiotimes.com/content/show-features/doctor-who/creating-the-weeping-angel/|work=[[Radio_Times|Radio Times]]|publisher=Exponent|accessdate=2012-08-08|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/61hZKx7IG?url=http://old.radiotimes.com/content/show-features/doctor-who/creating-the-weeping-angel/|archivedate=2011-09-14|date=6/2007|deadurl=yes}}</ref>。同時，為了使布朗斯卡和湯馬士看似一動也不動，劇組採用了數碼效果來彌補不足<ref name="commentary"/>。莫法特對哭泣天使的造型非常滿意，更直稱他們是「很棒的」<ref name="confidential"/>。穆里根也對哭泣天使的造型讚不絕口，並稱效果「實在太好」以及「真的嚇壞人」<ref name="confidential"/>。

==發行和反響==
《眨眼》於2007年6月9日晚上在英國BBC One首播。收視報告指，英國當晚共有662萬人通過電視收看這集<ref name="factfile"/>。儘管這集是《異世奇人》系列3中收視最低的一集，但劇集在[[欣賞指數|欣賞指數]]方面的得分是87，可被屬類為「出色」<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.barb.co.uk/whats-new/weekly-top-30?|title=Weekly Top 30 Programmes|publisher=Broadcasters' Audience Research Board|accessdate=2012-04-29|archive-date=2011-02-13|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/5wSLX6Azh?url=http://www.barb.co.uk/report/weeklyTopProgrammesOverview|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="factfile"/>。《眨眼》的[[DVD區域碼|第2區]]DVD於2007年7月23日與前兩集一併發行<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bbcshop.com/david-tennant/doctor-who-series-3-vol-3-dvd/invt/bbcdvd2383/|title=Doctor Who: Series 3 Vol.3|publisher=[[BBC|BBC]]|work=BBCShop|accessdate=2010-06-18|archive-date=2013-05-25|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6Gs4oyFix?url=http://www.bbcshop.com/david-tennant/doctor-who-series-3-vol-3-dvd/invt/bbcdvd2383/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。《異世奇人》系列3的DVD也收錄了這集，並在同年11月5日上市<ref>{{cite   web|url=http://www.bbcshop.com/david-tennant/doctor-who-complete-series-3-dvd/invt/bbcdvd2385/|title=Doctor Who: The Complete Series 3 (DVD)|publisher=[[BBC|BBC]]|work=BBCShop|accessdate=6-8-2012|archive-date=2013-05-25|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6Gs4qqxRy?url=http://www.bbcshop.com/david-tennant/doctor-who-complete-series-3-dvd/invt/bbcdvd2385/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

===專業評價===
《眨眼》取得不少的讚賞，《[[衛報|衛報]]》指儘管博士和鐘斯很少出場，但這集驚嚇程度十足，而且劇情十分合理。雜誌《[[SFX_(雜誌)|SFX]]》在5星為滿分下給了本集4顆星，並稱這集是歷年來最好、最可怕和最有智慧的《異世奇人》<ref>{{cite news|first=Stephen|last=Brook|url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/media/organgrinder/2007/jul/02/doctorwhoitsseasonfinalet|title=Doctor Who: it's season finale time!|newspaper=The Guardian|publisher=Guardian Media Group|date=2-6-2007|accessdate=2012-03-25|archive-date=2012-11-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121103224409/http://www.guardian.co.uk/media/organgrinder/2007/jul/02/doctorwhoitsseasonfinalet|dead-url=no}}</ref>。《[[IGN|IGN]]》在10分為滿分的基礎給了本集9.1分，大讚劇集以斯帕洛為重心的拍攝手法使觀眾能更了解該角色，並對穆里根出色的演技表示讚賞<ref name="IGN">{{cite journal|first=David|last=Bradley|url=http://www.sfx.co.uk/2007/06/09/doctor_who_3_10_blink/|title=Doctor Who 3.10 'Blink'|journal=SFX|publisher=Future Publishing|date=9-6-2007|accessdate=2012-03-25|archive-date=2014-01-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140113195108/http://www.sfx.co.uk/2007/06/09/doctor_who_3_10_blink/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。同時，《IGN》還對劇本的編寫感到滿意，「在短短的時間內，劇本不但能展示出角色們的關係，幾條時間線又能連成一線，那個新登場的可怕敵人竟可在博士不在場的情況下被打敗」<ref name="IGN"/>。總言之，這集是「很棒的」<ref name="IGN"/>。美國娛樂評論網絡刊物《[[偏鋒雜誌|偏鋒雜誌]]》（Slant Magazine）大讚《眨眼》不只是最出色的《異世奇人》劇集，更是一集超卓的科幻和恐怖劇集<ref name="Slant">{{cite web|first=Ross|last=Ruedinger|url=http://www.slantmagazine.com/house/2007/09/doctor-who-season-three-ep-10-blink/|title=Doctor Who, Season Three, Ep. 10:'Blink'|work=Slant Magazine|date=2007-09-15|access-date=2014-08-20|archive-date=2012-10-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121022162755/http://www.slantmagazine.com/house/2007/09/doctor-who-season-three-ep-10-blink/|dead-url=no}}</ref> 。此外，《偏鋒》還對劇集能在45分鐘內能交代錯綜複雜的劇情和人物特色感到讚嘆<ref name="Slant"/>。《[[每日電訊報|每日電訊報]]》云儘管這集是以斯帕洛為中心，但仍不止《眨眼》成為歷史上10部最好看的《異世奇人》劇集之一<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/culture/3674193/The-10-greatest-episodes-of-Doctor-Who-ever.html|title=The 10 Greatest Episodes of Doctor Who Ever|newspaper=The Daily Telegraph|publisher=Telegraph Media Group|date=2-7-2008|accessdate=11-2-2012|archive-date=2020-05-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200513072829/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/culture/3674193/The-10-greatest-episodes-of-Doctor-Who-ever.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

另一方面，雖然博士在今集出場的次數寥寥無幾，但他的演出還是得到認同。《IGN》在2010年評選出十大{{link-en|第十任博士}}出演的劇集，《眨眼》最終名列第6<ref>{{cite web|first=Matt|last=Wales|url=http://tv.ign.com/articles/105/1058228p2.html|title=Top 10 Tennant Doctor Who Stories|work=[[IGN|IGN]]|publisher=News Corporation|date=5-1-2010|accessdate=11-2-2012|archive-date=2013-05-25|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6Gs4tgRQq?url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2010/01/05/top-10-tennant-doctor-who-stories?page=2|dead-url=no}}</ref>。娛樂網站《TVOvermind》也在同年舉辦同類的選評，排名更高居第2<ref>{{cite web|first=Sam|last=McPherson|url=http://www.tvovermind.com/doctor-who/the-tenth-doctors-top-5-doctor-who-episodes/|title=The Tenth Doctor's Top 5 Doctor Who Episodes|publisher=TVOvermind|date=2-1-2010|accessdate=11-2-2012|archive-date=2012-04-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120404021848/http://www.tvovermind.com/doctor-who/the-tenth-doctors-top-5-doctor-who-episodes|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2011年，《[[哈芬登郵報|哈芬登郵報]]》在《異世奇人》{{link-en|系列6|Doctor Who (series 6)}}首播前選出5部適合新觀眾觀看的劇集，《眨眼》是其中之一<ref>{{cite web|first=Catherine|last=Lawson|url=http://www.aoltv.com/2011/08/09/doctor-who-5-essential-episodes/|title=Catch Up With 'Doctor Who': 5 Essential Episodes|work=The Huffington Post|date=9-8-2011|accessdate=11-2-2012|archive-date=2012-06-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120626184048/http://www.aoltv.com/2011/08/09/doctor-who-5-essential-episodes/|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。哭泣天使也獲得廣泛的好評。《SFX》於2009年選出21大《異世奇人》中最恐怖的劇集，《眨眼》位列榜首，筆者評論道﹕「一頭在你看不到的時候才會動的怪物已夠可怕，而在閃爍的燈光和斷斷續續的配樂親托下，場面變得更嚇人」<ref>{{cite journal|url=http://www.sfx.co.uk/2009/02/01/21_scariest_doctor_who_moments_7/|title=21 Scariest Doctor Who Moments 7|journal=SFX|publisher=Future Publishing|date=1-2-2009|accessdate=2012-04-14|archive-date=2013-01-11|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6DazzelKe?url=http://www.sfx.co.uk/2009/02/01/21_scariest_doctor_who_moments_7/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。作家[[尼爾·蓋曼|尼爾·蓋曼]]在《[[娛樂周刊|娛樂周刊]]》評選10個最經典的新怪物，哭泣天使排名第3<ref>{{Cite news|title=Neil Gaiman: My Top 10 New Classic Monsters|url=http://www.ew.com/ew/galler/0,,20213067_20213322_20214359_3,00.html|newspaper=Entertainment Weekly|publisher=Time Inc|date=7/2008|accessdate=7-8-2012}}{{Dead link}}</ref>。與此同時，《TV Squad》也把這外星生物評為電視史上最可怕怪物的第3位<ref>{{cite web|first=Annie|last=Wu|url=http://www.aoltv.com/2007/10/24/all-time-scariest-tv-characters-3-weeping-angels/|title=All-time scariest TV characters|work=TV Squad|publisher=Weblogs, Inc|date=2007-10-24|accessdate=7-8-2012|archive-date=2013-05-25|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6Gs4xFzdl?url=http://www.aoltv.com/2007/10/24/all-time-scariest-tv-characters-3-weeping-angels/|dead-url=yes}}</ref> 。在《每日電訊報》的一個評選中，哭泣天使被選為繼{{link-en|塑料人|Auton}}和[[戴立克|戴立克]]後最讓人不安的反派<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/culture/tvandradio/8493054/Doctor-Who-the-top-ten-baddies.html?image=7|title=Doctor Who – The Top Ten Baddies|newspaper=The Telegraph|publisher=Telegraph Media Group|accessdate=7-8-2012|location=London|date=4-5-2011|archive-date=2021-01-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210126103343/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/culture/tvandradio/8493054/Doctor-Who-the-top-ten-baddies.html?image=7|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2009年，《SFX》在對系列3的回顧中選出哭泣天使為系列中最令人喜愛的東西，並稱他們為永遠是最恐怖的怪物<ref>{{cite journal|url=http://www.sfx.co.uk/2009/02/01/27_things_sfx_loves_about_new_who_3/|title=27 Things SFX Loves About New Who 3|journal=SFX|publisher=Future Publishing|date=1-2-2009|accessdate=7-8-2012|archive-date=2013-01-11|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6Db037KQf?url=http://www.sfx.co.uk/2009/02/01/27_things_sfx_loves_about_new_who_3/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

===後續===
《眨眼》在播映後贏得多個的獎項，莫法特憑此集贏得[[英國電影和電視藝術學院|英國電影和電視藝術學院]]（BAFTA Craft）、威爾斯電影和電視藝術學院（BAFTA Cymru）最佳導演獎<ref name="bafta1">{{cite web |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/pressoffice/pressreleases/stories/2008/04_april/28/cymru.shtml |title=BAFTA Cymru success for BBC Wales |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] |date=2008-04-28 |accessdate=2008-05-13 |archive-date=2016-02-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160220114156/http://www.bbc.co.uk/pressoffice/pressreleases/stories/2008/04_april/28/cymru.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="bafta2">{{cite news |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/entertainment/7395593.stm |title=Bafta glory for Channel 4's Boy A |work=[[BBC_News_Online|BBC News Online]] |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] |date=12-5-2008 |accessdate=2008-05-13 |archive-date=2008-05-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080517174026/http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/entertainment/7395593.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，以及[[雨果獎|雨果獎]]最佳戲劇表現：短劇獎<ref name="Hugo">{{cite web |title=2008 Hugo Award Results Announced |url=http://www.thehugoawards.org/?p=146 |work=Hugo Award |publisher=World Science Fiction Society |date=9-8-2008 |accessdate=11-8-2008 |archive-date=2008-08-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080831234910/http://www.thehugoawards.org/?p=146 |dead-url=no }}</ref>﹔穆里根獲加拿大{{link-en|星座獎|Constellation Awards}}最佳女主角獎<ref>{{cite web |url=http://constellations.tcon.ca/2008.shtml |title=Looking Back At... The 2008 Constellation Awards |work=The Constellation Awards |publisher=TCON Promotional Society |date=2008-07-15 |access-date=2014-08-20 |archive-date=2014-07-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140726122405/http://constellations.tcon.ca/2008.shtml |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。劇集還獲提名為[[星雲獎|星雲獎]]最佳劇本獎，但最終未能得獎<ref name="nebula2">{{cite web |title = 2007 Nebula Award Winners |publisher = Science Fiction and Fantasy Writers of America, Inc |date = 2008-04-26 |url = http://www.sfwa.org/news/2008/07nebwiners.htm |accessdate = 2-6-2008 |deadurl = yes |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20080531095020/http://www.sfwa.org/news/2008/07nebwiners.htm |archivedate = 2008-05-31 }}</ref>。

同時，劇集和哭泣天使也得到觀眾的喜愛。《{{link-en|異世奇人雜誌|Doctor Who Magazine}}》於2007年向《眨眼》頒授最佳故事獎<ref>{{cite journal|title=2007 Awards|journal=Doctor Who Magazine|publisher=Panini Comics|location=Royal Tunbridge Wells, Kent|issue= 389|pages=40–41|date=2007-12-12}}</ref>。在兩年後，該雜誌發起調查，結果在6700名觀眾投票下，《眨眼》位列第2<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.theregister.co.uk/2009/09/17/best_who_ever/|title=''Doctor Who'' fans name best episode ever|first=Lester|last=Haines|work=The Register|publisher=Situation Publishing|date=2009-09-17|accessdate=11-2-2012|archive-date=2020-05-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200513072841/https://www.theregister.co.uk/2009/09/17/best_who_ever/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。BBC也舉行類似的投票，在2007年，電視台旗下的雜誌《異世奇人冒險記》發動年度最恐怖怪物投票。最終，逾1100名讀者選擇了哭泣天使，遠超於得票為300票的[[法師|法師]]及80票的[[戴立克|戴立克]]<ref>{{Cite web|title=Monster Hit|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080301231156/http://www.bbc.co.uk/doctorwho/news/cult/news/drwho/2007/09/12/48755.shtml|archivedate=2008年3月1日|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/doctorwho/news/cult/news/drwho/2007/09/12/48755.shtml|publisher=[[BBC|BBC]]|date=12-9-2007|accessdate=7-8-2012|deadurl=yes}}</ref>。2012年，《[[廣播時報|廣播時報]]》發起同樣的調查，在這1萬人參與的投票中，約一半的讀者選出哭泣天使為《異世奇人》最棒的怪物<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.radiotimes.com/news/2012-06-09/doctor-who-weeping-angels-beat-the-daleks-to-be-voted-fans-favourite-ever-monsters|title=Doctor Who: Weeping Angels beat The Daleks to be voted fans' favourite ever monsters|work=Radio Times|publisher=Exponent|last=Jones|first=Paul|date=9-6-2012|accessdate=7-8-2012|archive-date=2013-05-25|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6Gs53Km5O?url=http://www.radiotimes.com/news/2012-06-09/doctor-who-weeping-angels-beat-the-daleks-to-be-voted-fans-favourite-ever-monsters|dead-url=no}}</ref>。莫法特之後還在系列5中寫出以哭泣天使為題材的合集—《[[天使時代|天使時代]]》/《[[肉與石|肉與石]]》。憑這兩集，莫法特成為《異世奇人》的首席編劇<ref>{{cite web|first=Steven|last=Moffat|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/blogs/tv/2010/04/doctor-who-the-return-of-the-w.shtml|title=Doctor Who: The return of the Weeping Angels|publisher=[[BBC|BBC]]|date=2010-04-22|accessdate=7-8-2012|archive-date=2011-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111112164114/http://www.bbc.co.uk/blogs/tv/2010/04/doctor-who-the-return-of-the-w.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>。之後，哭泣天使還分別在系列7的《[[哭泣天使佔領曼哈頓|哭泣天使佔領曼哈頓]]》、短劇{{link-en|至善如金|Good as Gold}}和小說《被天使觸到》（Touched by an Angel）登場<ref>{{cite web|first=Paul|last=Jones|url=http://www.radiotimes.com/news/2012-05-24/weeping-angels-to-feature-tonight-in-brand-new-doctor-who-adventure|title=Weeping Angels to feature tonight in brand-new Doctor Who adventure|publisher=[[BBC|BBC]]|date=2012-05-24|accessdate=7-8-2012|archive-date=2013-05-25|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6Gs58r4OR?url=http://www.radiotimes.com/news/2012-05-24/weeping-angels-to-feature-tonight-in-brand-new-doctor-who-adventure|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

劇中一些台詞也成為經典。其中，博士說「天使們把電話亭拿走」（The angels have the phone box）後，拉里隨即說他把這句印在[[T恤|T恤]]上，這 
段對白不久後成為名句，並真的被人印在衣服上兜售。網上零售店如ThinkGeek和Zazzle也有出售相關的產品<ref name="commentary">{{cite video|people=Steven Moffat, Murray Gold|date=9-6-2007|title=Blink: Episode Commentary|location=Doctor Who: The Complete Third Series|medium=DVD|publisher=BBC Video}}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url= http://www.thinkgeek.com/interests/exclusives/e78d/ | title= The Angels Have the Phone Box | work= ThinkGeek | publisher= Geeknet | accessdate= 4-5-2011 | archive-date= 2013-05-24 | archive-url= https://www.webcitation.org/6Gqu7gw5Z?url=http://www.thinkgeek.com/product/e78d/ | dead-url= no }}</ref>。另外，博士那句「時間和波浪，變化無常」（wibbly-wobbly timey-wimey）的台詞也成了名言。此後莫法特在《{{link-en|同去刺殺希特拉|Let's Kill Hitler}}》和《[[宇宙大爆炸|宇宙大爆炸]]》也有引述此句來說明於《異世奇人》中複雜而混亂的時間線<ref>{{cite news|first=Michael|last=Hogan|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/culture/tvandradio/doctor-who/8725946/Doctor-Who-Lets-Kill-Hitler-BBC-One-review.html|title=Doctor Who, Let's Kill Hitler, BBC One, review|newspaper=The Daily Telegraph|publisher=Telegraph Media Group|date=2011-08-27|accessdate=7-8-2012|archive-date=2013-01-12|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6DbaQpPIm?url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/culture/tvandradio/doctor-who/8725946/Doctor-Who-Lets-Kill-Hitler-BBC-One-review.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|first=Dan|last=Martin|url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/tv-and-radio/tvandradioblog/2011/aug/27/doctor-who-television|title=Doctor Who: Let's Kill Hitler — series 32, episode 8|newspaper=The Guardian|publisher=Guardian Media Group|date=2011-08-27|accessdate=7-8-2012|archive-date=2013-01-12|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6DbaPtzXS?url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/tv-and-radio/tvandradioblog/2011/aug/27/doctor-who-television|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2012年，[[英國廣播公司美國台|BBC America]]製作一套關於系列4的特輯，其中就有一部片段稱為「異世奇人之變化無常」<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.denofgeek.com/tv/doctor-who/22129/new-doctor-who-docs-coming-to-bbc-america | title = New Doctor Who docs coming to BBC America | first = Louisa | last = Muller | date = 2012-07-25 | accessdate = 2012-08-23 | publisher = [[Den_of_Geek|Den of Geek]] | archive-date = 2013-05-25 | archive-url = https://www.webcitation.org/6Gs5CuYec?url=http://www.denofgeek.com/tv/doctor-who/22129/new-doctor-who-docs-coming-to-bbc-america | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

《眨眼》甚至出現衍生歌曲。英國搖滾樂隊Chameleon Circuit與歌手阿歷斯迪及[[查理·麥克唐納|查理·麥克唐納]]等人創出一首關於本集的歌，名字同樣為《眨眼》。這歌曲也收錄在同名的唱片中<ref>{{cite web|last=Newitz|first=Annalee|authorlink=Annalee Newitz|title=It's Not Filk – It's Trock!|url=http://io9.com/5086730/its-not-filk-+-its-trock|work=i09|publisher=Gawker Media|accessdate=7 August 2012|date=14 November 2008|archive-date=2012-09-13|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6AeB2ukg5?url=http://io9.com/5086730/its-not-filk-+-its-trock|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite AV media notes |title= Chameleon Circuit|titlelink= |others=Chameleon Circuit |year=2009 |publisher= DFTBA Records}}</ref>。

